hese structured instances of\nMin-Plus-Convolution can be solved in time $O(n^{1.5})$ [Chi,Duan,Xie,Zhang\n'22] (in contrast to the conjectured $n^{2-o(1)}$ lower bound for the general\ncase).\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 17 May 2022 17:08:30 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-05-18"}
