ep.\nThis also prevents erroneous designs from having to be (partially) redone,\nwhich is also costly and burdensome. To validate our proposal, we implemented a\npreliminary reasoner under CLP(Q/R) and ASP with constraints and evaluated it\nwith several BIM models. Under consideration for acceptance in Theory and\nPractice of Logic Programming (TPLP).\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 17 May 2022 18:22:57 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-05-19"}
