derated self-supervised pre-training methods yield models that generalize\nbetter to out-of-distribution data and perform more effectively when\nfine-tuning with limited labeled data, compared to existing FL algorithms. The\ncode is available at https://github.com/rui-yan/SSL-FL.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 17 May 2022 18:33:43 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 11 Jan 2023 07:30:24 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-01-12"}
