 not regulate the type of spiral arm\nhosted by a galaxy. Our results may have important implications for formation\nand evolution of spiral arms in galaxies.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 18 May 2022 05:54:07 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 29 Jun 2022 05:23:03 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 25 Oct 2022 06:33:11 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-11-30"}
